@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title AIPOT User Scenario (가입/플레이/AI복기)

actor User
participant "Frontend\n(React)" as FE
participant "Auth API" as Auth
participant "Lobby API" as Lobby
participant "Rooms API" as Rooms
participant "Game API" as Game
participant "GameService" as GameSvc
participant "StoreService" as Store
participant "HandReview API" as Review
participant "HandReviewService" as ReviewSvc
participant "AiService" as AI
participant "LLM Provider" as LLM

== 1) 인증 & 매칭 ==
User -> FE : 로그인/회원가입/게스트 선택
FE -> Auth : POST /auth/sign-in (or sign-up, guest-session)
Auth --> FE : accessToken + user profile

User -> FE : Quick Play 클릭
FE -> Lobby : POST /lobby/quick-play
Lobby -> Store : 참가 가능한 공개 룸 탐색 + 착석 처리
Store --> Lobby : roomId
Lobby --> FE : matched=true, roomId
FE -> Rooms : GET /rooms/{roomId}
Rooms --> FE : room detail

== 2) 플레이 루프 & BOT 행동 ==
loop 상태 동기화
  FE -> Game : GET /game/rooms/{roomId}/state
  Game -> GameSvc : getState(user, roomId)
  GameSvc -> Store : autoResolveTimeout(roomId)

  alt 현재 턴이 BOT
    GameSvc -> AI : generateBotAction(context, role)
    AI -> LLM : provider call (local/openai/claude/gemini)
    LLM --> AI : JSON action
    AI --> GameSvc : normalized decision
    GameSvc -> Store : applyPlayerAction(bot)
  end

  GameSvc --> Game : snapshot
  Game --> FE : room/game snapshot
end

User -> FE : fold/check/call/bet/raise/all-in
FE -> Game : POST /game/rooms/{roomId}/act
Game -> Store : applyPlayerAction(human)
Game -> GameSvc : processBotTurns(roomId)
GameSvc -> Store : 필요 시 BOT 후속 액션 처리
Game --> FE : updated state

== 3) 핸드 리뷰 비동기 분석 (PRO) ==
User -> FE : Hand Review 진입 + Analyze 클릭
FE -> Review : POST /hand-review/hands/{handId}/analyze
Review -> ReviewSvc : analyze(user, handId, dto)
ReviewSvc -> Store : analyzeJob = pending
Review --> FE : queued(requestId)

par 백그라운드 분석
  ReviewSvc -> Store : analyzeJob = running
  ReviewSvc -> AI : analyzeAllHandActions(handContext, heroUserId)
  AI -> LLM : structured action review request
  LLM --> AI : summary + action reviews(JSON/텍스트)
  AI --> ReviewSvc : normalized reviews(ev/equity/mix)
  loop action별 저장
    ReviewSvc -> Store : addHandActionAnalysis(...)
  end
  ReviewSvc -> Store : analyzeJob = completed
else 클라이언트 폴링
  loop every 3s
    FE -> Review : GET /hand-review/hands/{handId}/analyze-status
    Review -> Store : getAnalyzeJob
    Review --> FE : pending/running/completed/failed
  end
end

FE -> Review : GET /hand-review/hands/{handId}
Review -> Store : hand detail + analyses 조회
Review --> FE : replay + action insight + GTO mix 시각화 데이터

note right of AI
- 히어로 관점 강제
- 언어별 출력 제약(en/ko/ja)
- 누락 액션 보강(2차 요청 + 로컬 폴백)
- provider 실패 시 결정적 fallback
end note

@enduml
